LEVEL4 {TRUEIP - Proxy Protocol Configuration}

 TRUEIP adds PROXY Protocol v1 support so the BBS can see
 real client IPs when behind a reverse proxy.

TPORT {Proxy listener port 2324} N 1 65535

 TCP port for PROXY-wrapped connections.

REQHDR {Require PROXY header? YES} B

 YES = reject connections without a valid PROXY header.

TRUSTIP {Trusted proxy IPs (comma-sep) } S 64 Trusted IPs

 IP addresses of your reverse proxy. Comma-separated.

MAXRATE {Max connections/sec 10} N 0 999

 Rate limit on proxy port. 0 = no limit.

LOGEN {Enable debug file log? NO} B

 Write detailed trace to TRUEIP.LOG.

LOGMAX {Max log size (KB) 1024} (LOGEN=YES) N 0 99999

 Log rotation threshold.

